firefox driver should be saved to the 'drivers' folder and named as 'geckodriver'
may be downloaded from 'https://github.com/mozilla/geckodriver/releases'

running from command line: mvn clean test -Dsuite=openAllPages.xml

folder with full logs, screenshots and page sources: /target/debug-log/
(it can be configured in resources/settings.properties)

ReportNG report is created here: /target/surefire-reports/